criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  (Suspected) Lung Cancer

          -  For malignancy suspected LAG on imaging (enlarged based on CT and/or FDG avid based on
             FDG-PET);

          -  Indication for endosonographic mediastinal staging by EBUS;

          -  Indication for LAG sampling;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Contraindication for EUS;

          -  Pregnancy;
